title: Writing, Part 1 Practice Test 2
intro_text:
Writing, Part 1

Welcome to the Writing, Part 1 Practice Test!

Take your time with this test. If you don't know how to answer a question, leave it blank and go on to the next question. Guessing is a good idea on the GED, but for this test, we really want to understand what you know. If you are unsure of an answer and want to think about it, you can click “Review Question Later” to come back to the question later.

There are 25 questions on the test. These questions will give you practice with the types of questions you will see on the GED.

Relax and do your best!
